name: Touhou: Labyrinthian Busters
description:
Touhou: Trouble in the Labyrinth is a short tale of Reimu and Marisa travelling through a secret underground labyrinth they've uncovered. Exciting adventure awaits them!

This game is broke af, do come back in a few days if you want to see a post-game jam build! 

Otherwise, RATE US HARD BABY
